2003-09-09 Marc Delisle  <lem9@users.sourceforge.net>
    * libraries/mysql_wrappers.lib.php3: bug 795443: wrong results coming
      from mysql_list_tables, so modify PMA_mysql_list_tables to use
      SHOW TABLES FROM

