    * server_*.php3:
      - The messages are now displayed by server_links.inc.php3, so
        server_common.inc.php3 may be included earlier;
      - Beautified code.
    * server_privileges.php3:
      - Wrong GRANT syntax;
      - Changed the default behavior of the for fields "pred_username" and
        "pred_password".

